---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import BorderBeam from '../../components/magic/BorderBeam.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<BaseLayout title="项目 | 李卓衡" description="Data and analytics projects">
  <h1 class="page-title" data-i18n="sectionProjects">项目</h1>

  <!-- 个人项目 -->
  <section class="project-section">
    <h2 class="section-subtitle content-zh">个人项目</h2>
    <h2 class="section-subtitle content-en">Personal Projects</h2>
    <div class="project-grid">
      <a href={`${base}projects/crawler/`} class="project-card-link">
        <BorderBeam class="project-card-wrap">
          <article class="project-card">
            <h3 class="project-title content-zh">动态爬虫与数据采集平台</h3>
            <h3 class="project-title content-en">Dynamic Web Crawler & Data Collection Platform</h3>
            <div class="content-zh"><p>使用 <strong>Selenium + BeautifulSoup</strong> 搭建可复用动态页爬虫，支持无限滚动与复杂 DOM；设计标准化 <strong>ETL</strong> 清洗/解析并写入 <strong>MySQL/PostgreSQL</strong>。</p></div>
            <div class="content-en"><p>Built a reusable crawler for dynamic pages using <strong>Selenium + BeautifulSoup</strong>, supporting infinite scroll and complex DOM structures. Designed a standardized <strong>ETL pipeline</strong>.</p></div>
            <span class="view-detail content-zh">查看详情 →</span>
            <span class="view-detail content-en">View details →</span>
          </article>
        </BorderBeam>
      </a>
      <a href={`${base}projects/game-market/`} class="project-card-link">
        <BorderBeam class="project-card-wrap">
          <article class="project-card">
            <h3 class="project-title content-zh">游戏市场数据分析与预测系统</h3>
            <h3 class="project-title content-en">Computer Game Market Data Analysis & Forecasting System</h3>
            <div class="content-zh"><p>基于 <strong>PostgreSQL</strong> 自动化采集与存储；特征工程与多模型预测（<strong>Random Forest、Gradient Boosting、ARIMA、Prophet</strong>）；输出 7 日预测与风险区间。</p></div>
            <div class="content-en"><p>Automated data ingestion with <strong>PostgreSQL</strong>. Feature engineering + multi-model forecasting (<strong>Random Forest, Gradient Boosting, ARIMA, Prophet</strong>). Delivered <strong>7-day forecasts</strong> and risk intervals.</p></div>
            <span class="view-detail content-zh">查看详情 →</span>
            <span class="view-detail content-en">View details →</span>
          </article>
        </BorderBeam>
      </a>
      <a href={`${base}projects/ecommerce-analytics/`} class="project-card-link">
        <BorderBeam class="project-card-wrap">
          <article class="project-card">
            <h3 class="project-title content-zh">电商用户与营销分析</h3>
            <h3 class="project-title content-en">E-commerce User & Marketing Analytics</h3>
            <div class="content-zh"><p>搭建 KPI 体系（UV/PV、漏斗转化、留存、复购）；<strong>RFM + K-means</strong> 用户分群，识别高价值与流失风险用户。</p></div>
            <div class="content-en"><p>Built KPI system (UV/PV, funnel conversion, retention, repurchase). Segmented users via <strong>RFM + K-means</strong>, identifying high-value and churn-risk groups.</p></div>
            <span class="view-detail content-zh">查看详情 →</span>
            <span class="view-detail content-en">View details →</span>
          </article>
        </BorderBeam>
      </a>
      <a href={`${base}projects/operations-product-analytics/`} class="project-card-link">
        <BorderBeam class="project-card-wrap">
          <article class="project-card">
            <h3 class="project-title content-zh">运营与选品分析项目</h3>
            <h3 class="project-title content-en">Operations & Product Selection Analytics</h3>
            <div class="content-zh"><p>整合多业务系统数据，构建选品指标框架（销量、销售额、增长率、转化率、退款率等）；输出每日运营简报。</p></div>
            <div class="content-en"><p>Integrated multi-system data to build a product selection metrics framework. Delivered daily operations briefs for rapid decision-making.</p></div>
            <span class="view-detail content-zh">查看详情 →</span>
            <span class="view-detail content-en">View details →</span>
          </article>
        </BorderBeam>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 校园及社会项目 -->
  <section class="project-section">
    <h2 class="section-subtitle content-zh">校园及社会项目</h2>
    <h2 class="section-subtitle content-en">Campus & Social Projects</h2>
    <div class="project-grid">
      <a href={`${base}projects/nasa-space-apps/`} class="project-card-link">
        <BorderBeam class="project-card-wrap">
          <article class="project-card">
            <h3 class="project-title content-zh">NASA Space Apps Challenge — 小行星撞击模拟平台</h3>
            <h3 class="project-title content-en">NASA Space Apps Challenge — Asteroid Impact Simulation</h3>
            <div class="content-zh"><p>基于 NASA 开放数据的交互式小行星撞击模拟与分析平台；负责 Prediction 模块，实现 API 接入与可视化联动。</p></div>
            <div class="content-en"><p>Web-based interactive asteroid impact simulation platform using NASA open data. Led the Prediction module: API integration and visualization linkage.</p></div>
            <span class="view-detail content-zh">查看详情 →</span>
            <span class="view-detail content-en">View details →</span>
          </article>
        </BorderBeam>
      </a>
      <a href={`${base}projects/social-salary/`} class="project-card-link">
        <BorderBeam class="project-card-wrap">
          <article class="project-card">
            <h3 class="project-title content-zh">社交网络与起薪分析</h3>
            <h3 class="project-title content-en">Social Networks & Starting Salary Analysis</h3>
            <div class="content-zh"><p>基于问卷数据构建分析数据集；描述统计、分组比较与相关分析探索社交网络使用与结果的关系。</p></div>
            <div class="content-en"><p>Built an analysis dataset from survey data. Used descriptive stats and correlation analysis to explore links between social network usage and outcomes.</p></div>
            <span class="view-detail content-zh">查看详情 →</span>
            <span class="view-detail content-en">View details →</span>
          </article>
        </BorderBeam>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <p class="page-footer"><a href={base}>← <span data-i18n="navHome">首页</span></a></p>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-title { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; }
  .project-section { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .section-subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    color: var(--text);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
  }
  .project-grid { display: grid; gap: 1.25rem; }
  .project-card-link {
    display: block;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }
  .project-card-link:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .project-card-wrap {
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 2px;
    background: var(--glass-bg);
    backdrop-filter: blur(var(--glass-blur));
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(var(--glass-blur));
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    box-shadow: var(--glass-shadow);
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }
  .project-card-link:hover .project-card-wrap {
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }
  .project-card {
    background: rgba(22, 27, 34, 0.35);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    border-radius: calc(var(--radius) - 2px);
    padding: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 0;
    box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }
  .project-title { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 0.5rem; color: var(--text); }
  .project-card .content-zh p, .project-card .content-en p { margin: 0 0 0.75rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }
  .view-detail {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .project-card-link:hover .view-detail {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  .page-footer { margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); }
</style>
